4. Unit Test Examples
4.1 Employee Onboarding Test
def test_onboard_employee():
    service = EmployeeLifecycleService(db_session)

    employee = service.onboard_employee(test_employee)

    assert employee.id == "EMP_TEST_001"
    assert employee.status.value == "ACTIVE"
4.2 Access Provisioning Test
def test_access_provisioning():
    service = EmployeeLifecycleService(db_session)

    service.onboard_employee(test_employee)

    access = db_session.query(AccessRecord).filter_by(
        employee_id="EMP_TEST_001"
    ).first()

    assert access.is_active is True
4.3 Offboarding Test
def test_offboarding():
    service = EmployeeLifecycleService(db_session)

    service.offboard_employee("EMP_TEST_001")

    employee = db_session.query(Employee).get("EMP_TEST_001")

    assert employee.status.value == "EXITED"
5. Integration Testing
5.1 HR → Workflow Engine
def test_hr_to_workflow_trigger():
    event = {
        "type": "NEW_HIRE",
        "payload": test_employee
    }

    response = workflow_controller.handle_event(
        event["type"], event["payload"]
    )

    assert response.id == "EMP_TEST_001"
5.2 Workflow → IAM System
def test_iam_provisioning():
    employee = service.onboard_employee(test_employee)

    assert external_iam_system.user_exists(employee.email)
6. Access Control Testing
6.1 Unauthorized Access Test
def test_access_denied():
    acl = AccessControlService(db_session)

    result = acl.has_permission(
        user_id="random_user",
        action="DELETE_EMPLOYEE",
        resource="EMPLOYEE"
    )

    assert result is False
6.2 Authorized Access Test
def test_access_allowed():
    acl = AccessControlService(db_session)

    result = acl.has_permission(
        user_id="hr_admin_01",
        action="CREATE_EMPLOYEE",
        resource="EMPLOYEE"
    )

    assert result is True
7. Security Testing Scenarios
7.1 Role Escalation Attempt
Try assigning admin role via API without permission
Expected: ❌ Rejected (403 Forbidden)
7.2 Token Expiry Test
Use expired session token
Expected: ❌ Authentication failure
7.3 Data Injection Test
Attempt SQL injection in employee fields
Expected: ❌ Input sanitized / blocked
8. End-to-End Test Flow
Onboarding Flow
Create employee in HR system
Trigger NEW_HIRE event
Verify:
Employee created
Email generated
Access provisioned
Tasks assigned
Audit logs written
Offboarding Flow
Trigger exit approval
System executes:
